display_name.description: User-friendly name to use in a UI to display the namespace name.

objects.description: Object definitions, if any, for the namespace.

namespace.description: The namespace is unique across all users.

visibility.description: Namespace visibility. Public or private. Default is private.

protected.description:
Namespace protection for deletion. Valid value is true or false.
Default is false.

resource_type_associations.description: Resource types, if any, that are associated with this namespace

properties.description: Property definitions, if any, for the namespace.
